          </li>
          <li class="menu">
            <img src="/images/后台管理UI素材/切图/icon_banner.png" alt="">
            <a href="/courseGrade" target="right">课程成绩</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li>
        <div class="menu">
